Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.92,0:00:14.93,Show Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs142.5\fnGallow Tree\4aFF\pos(443.949,598.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.15,0:00:15.24,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.91,0:00:18.79,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,with its armies\Nstraight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.45,0:00:23.12,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows\Nthreaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.12,0:00:26.75,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.75,0:00:30.51,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.51,0:00:33.68,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.05,0:00:36.80,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.80,0:00:40.27,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.35,0:00:44.94,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.94,0:00:48.44,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.44,0:00:51.07,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.15,0:00:54.65,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.82,0:00:59.45,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.45,0:01:02.79,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.30,0:01:11.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji Hayato is the Kamen\NRider, a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.14,0:01:13.27,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was modified by the evil\NShocker, a secret
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.27,0:01:15.13,Narrator,,0,0,0,,organization plotting\Nworld domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.13,0:01:18.77,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider has pledged to\Nfight Shocker and free humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.50,0:01:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And... go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.12,0:01:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You're losing speed!\NPick up the pace!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.36,0:01:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Fifteen seconds left!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.88,0:01:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.55,0:01:58.39,Narrator,,0,0,0,,A swimmer practicing for the Olympics\Ndisappeared in front of his team's eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.98,0:02:03.92,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Days passed with no sign of this\Nstrange mystery ever being solved.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.24,0:02:09.25,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs185\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\1c&HF3F4F4&\b1\pos(487.167,300.389)}Monstrous Merman
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.24,0:02:09.25,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs215\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\1c&HF3F4F4&\b1\pos(487.167,650.389)}Amazonia
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.08,0:02:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker has to be behind this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.87,0:02:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But why would they\Ngo after a swimmer?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.34,0:02:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't see anything\Nout of the ordinary.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.05,0:02:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.87,0:02:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing off here, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.06,0:02:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.31,0:02:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You think HQ got their\Ninformation wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.21,0:02:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Definitely not.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.22,0:02:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This is definitely the place the\Nmystery sound waves were coming from.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.82,0:02:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.45,0:02:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If the FBI sent an\Nexpert like you,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.42,0:02:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,they must be sure of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.28,0:03:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's try another dive tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.04,0:03:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.83,0:03:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready, Miyuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.12,0:03:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch carefully how your\Nbig brother does it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.16,0:03:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay very calm and move\Nyour arms and legs slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.94,0:03:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But deep water is scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.91,0:03:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't talk like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.07,0:03:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't learn to swim\Nproperly in shallow water.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.45,0:03:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.06,0:03:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.49,0:03:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,He's such a good swimmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.98,0:03:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Miyuki!\NSwim over to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.61,0:03:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry! I'll be right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.15,0:03:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyuki? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.86,0:03:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Swim to...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.13,0:03:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.56,0:04:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone help!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.05,0:04:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.68,0:04:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone help!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.58,0:04:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.88,0:04:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.58,0:04:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get you for that,\Nyou filthy tomboys!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.76,0:04:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Catch me if you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.24,0:04:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait for me! Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.54,0:04:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.54,0:04:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.23,0:04:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with you, Mari?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.63,0:04:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You're looking kind of down...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.21,0:04:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You homesick or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.53,0:04:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine. Just leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.57,0:04:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,See? She yelled at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.08,0:04:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Kids should stay out\Nof grown-ups' business.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.96,0:04:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.68,0:05:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut it out! Hey, cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.94,0:05:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!\NI think it's time for lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.78,0:05:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki and the others\Nshould be back soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.71,0:05:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Who cares what Mr. Taki does?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.36,0:05:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,He went off with another girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.16,0:05:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That woman's a co-worker.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.26,0:05:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't sweat it, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.62,0:05:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But Mr. Taki promised he'd\Nteach me how to dive next time
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.42,0:05:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,we were at the beach...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.45,0:05:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, I see someone over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.17,0:05:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.35,0:05:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go look.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.79,0:05:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.85,0:05:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,My brother's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.30,0:05:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't cry, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.45,0:05:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you get separated?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.01,0:05:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,He was eaten by a monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.96,0:05:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.05,0:05:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell us more!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.14,0:06:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,This man possesses\Nconsiderable stamina.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.18,0:06:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We should transform him\Ninto a worker at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.38,0:06:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazonia.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.27,0:06:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Is your mission, Operation:\N507, proceeding as planned?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.66,0:06:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It will surely be\Ncomplete by the deadline.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.68,0:06:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But the workers are exhausted\Nby the labor on the sea floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.00,0:06:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Continue to catch humans\Nwith exceptional stamina
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.31,0:06:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and complete the operation\Nas quickly as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.06,0:06:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And when it is done, there will be none\Nwho can oppose the power of Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.37,0:06:47.60,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Evil organization\NShocker had set its eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.60,0:06:51.96,Narrator,,0,0,0,,on a large uranium deposit\Nin the ocean near Japan,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.96,0:06:54.51,Narrator,,0,0,0,,and were advancing a plan to\Nbuild an undersea factory.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.06,0:06:59.11,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They refer to this\Nplan as Operation: 507.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.31,0:07:10.49,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile,\Nbelieving the swimmer's mysterious
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.49,0:07:13.32,Narrator,,0,0,0,,disappearance to be\Nthe work of Shocker,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.32,0:07:15.78,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji Hayato was\Nout investigating.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.45,0:07:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.06,0:07:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The water from the pool\Nflows directly to the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.57,0:07:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,They kidnapped that swimmer to create\Na cyborg proficient in the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.29,0:07:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Damnable Shocker...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.87,0:07:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you scheming\Nfor our oceans now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.58,0:07:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It showed up around here, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.87,0:07:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It has to be a Shocker cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.09,0:07:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to get to the\Nbottom of their plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.28,0:07:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,A sea monster this time, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.35,0:08:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll do an early dive tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.48,0:08:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure we'll learn\Nsomething useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.92,0:08:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll start from the\Nopposite side as Taki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.77,0:08:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Between the undersea monster\Nand the mysterious sound waves,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.16,0:08:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,they clearly have an\Nunderwater base in the area.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.14,0:08:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But I wonder what our\NHayato's getting up to...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.08,0:08:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato should join us soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.20,0:08:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.40,0:09:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are, monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.73,0:09:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.70,0:10:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll face you, Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.86,0:10:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.22,0:10:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato should have\Nbeen here by now...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.37,0:11:59.30,Bumper Episode 14-51,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs85\pos(321,454)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.71,0:12:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll meet back here\Nin twenty minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.29,0:12:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.54,0:12:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.89,0:12:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget the emergency\Nsignal if there's trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.39,0:12:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.39,0:12:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, where's Hayato, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.32,0:12:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder where he could be...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.83,0:12:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think something\Nhappened to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.87,0:12:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.19,0:12:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.54,0:12:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.25,0:12:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hayato. You sure took\Nyour time getting here...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.90,0:12:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes,\NI ran into Shocker on the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.21,0:13:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What?\NThey showed themselves already?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.56,0:13:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a fearsome\Nfoe, a fish monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.50,0:13:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It completely had the\Nadvantage in the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.73,0:13:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,A fish monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.55,0:13:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But then Taki and his\Npartner are in trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.01,0:13:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Where have they gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.22,0:13:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,They went for an\Nearly morning dive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.01,0:13:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.80,0:13:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki doesn't stand a\Nchance against that thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.76,0:13:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm heading out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.82,0:13:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Tachibana, all of you.\NStay in the hotel room.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.52,0:13:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.09,0:13:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.86,0:13:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll save my big\Nbrother, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.23,0:13:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyuki, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.31,0:13:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.98,0:13:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise,\NI'll bring your brother back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.31,0:13:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinky swear?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.95,0:13:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinky swear.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.75,0:13:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you worry.\NHe'll save him, no sweat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.57,0:13:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Within the next 24 hours, you'll be\Nready for labor on the ocean floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.43,0:14:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you...\Nwhat are you doing to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.02,0:14:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.55,0:14:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You... are you with Shocker?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.22,0:15:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki's in danger...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.55,0:15:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Taki?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.16,0:15:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Bad news!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.02,0:15:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,He activated the\Nemergency signal!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.28,0:15:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Was I too late?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.57,0:15:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, leave Taki to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.40,0:15:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.39,0:15:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You return to the hotel\Nand protect the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.16,0:15:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll be in danger, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.02,0:15:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.34,0:15:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We've captured the spy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.90,0:15:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You dare to stand against\Nus, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.76,0:16:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's the uranium\Nyou're after?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.26,0:16:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you work with the Rider?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.33,0:16:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazonia.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.63,0:16:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That man is Taki of the FBI.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.54,0:16:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,His partner and the Kamen\NRider are both on the move.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.90,0:16:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Capture them at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.09,0:16:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Put that man into the capsule.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.52,0:17:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn... they captured her, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.88,0:17:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Put that woman in the capsule.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.02,0:17:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll lure the\NKamen Rider to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.26,0:17:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kamen Rider is\Ninside the base!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.07,0:17:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it! All of you, stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.25,0:17:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Let him come to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.67,0:17:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's odd...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.82,0:18:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What are they planning?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.69,0:18:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.57,0:18:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki! Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.47,0:18:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.22,0:18:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But they seem to have something planned.\NBe careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.21,0:18:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.16,0:18:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.99,0:18:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.74,0:18:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, I'm going to\Nbreak your capsule.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.38,0:18:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Now her!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.75,0:18:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.03,0:18:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are, Kamen Rider...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.70,0:18:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This place will be your grave.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.03,0:18:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.09,0:18:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.21,0:18:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.31,0:19:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider... are you sure\Nyou want to fight here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.27,0:19:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.86,0:19:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Strange... it's hard to breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.49,0:19:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Having trouble, Rider?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.13,0:19:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I've set the oxygen in this room\Nto one-third of its usual levels!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.42,0:19:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Die, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.01,0:19:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Those switches...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.27,0:20:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider...\Nwe'll finish this later.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.16,0:20:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Withdraw!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.72,0:20:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll find Mr. Aoyagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.09,0:20:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.22,0:20:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Thanks.\NI'll detonate their base.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.18,0:20:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.59,0:20:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.69,0:20:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.70,0:20:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.07,0:20:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.57,0:20:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.48,0:20:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.17,0:20:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, you're safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.84,0:20:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I managed to make it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.65,0:20:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What about my brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.57,0:20:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.\NThe Kamen Rider is going to save him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.36,0:20:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.02,0:21:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right, Mr. Aoyagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.38,0:21:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.10,0:21:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll jump straight\Nto the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.41,0:21:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider...\NI've been waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.74,0:21:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Aoyagi, Miyuki is waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.53,0:21:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.75,0:22:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider...\Nfinally giving up the ghost?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.24,0:22:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.10,0:22:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.37,0:22:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider won!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.19,0:22:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.59,0:22:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.84,0:22:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.72,0:22:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.66,0:22:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew you were alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.77,0:22:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry to worry you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.31,0:22:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kamen Rider saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.85,0:22:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.40,0:22:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really glad your brother's\Nback, Miyuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.99,0:22:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better spoil her for a\Nwhile, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.87,0:22:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.46,0:22:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,She was really worried about\Nyou, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.99,0:22:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.80,0:23:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got me crying, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.49,0:23:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.55,0:23:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.33,0:23:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.42,0:23:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.62,0:23:29.63,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji Hayato has defeated his\Nlatest unspeakably powerful foe.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.92,0:23:35.80,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But Shocker's unwavering persistence\Nonly renews his will to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.16,0:23:40.76,Cont,,0,0,0,,{\blur.8\fad(0,480)}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.06,0:23:42.93,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\4aFF\bord0\b1\fs67.5\fnCalibri\pos(499.031,496.481)}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.06,0:23:44.51,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The next assassin sent by Shocker\NHQ to kill our Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.51,0:23:46.45,Narrator,,0,0,0,,is the soaring monster\NMusasabeedle.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.45,0:23:49.28,Narrator,,0,0,0,,When Hayato and the others catch wind\Nof Shocker's plan to blow up Sapporo,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.28,0:23:50.70,Narrator,,0,0,0,,they head to Hokkaido.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.70,0:23:52.99,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They arrive at Lake Toya on Mount\NShowa-Shinzan.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.99,0:23:55.72,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's a fabulous location\Nshoot in midsummer Hokkaido!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.72,0:23:59.73,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Join us next week for "Soaring\NMonster Musasabeedle."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.26,0:24:01.02,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs115\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\1c&HF3F4F4&\b1\pos(487.167,700.389)}Soaring Monster \NMusasabeedle
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.34,0:24:11.18,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,He came here on a storm...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.76,0:24:13.76,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is he? Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.76,0:24:15.72,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is this man of storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.72,0:24:18.77,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,who sends the\Nvillains scattering?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.27,0:24:21.14,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.14,0:24:23.02,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,His mask stands for justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.02,0:24:24.81,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Start it up! Rev it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.81,0:24:26.15,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Get that engine running!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.61,0:24:28.65,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Give me top speed, Cyclone!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.70,0:24:34.37,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Hit them with\Nall of your anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.37,0:24:37.95,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Put an end to Shocker's evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.95,0:24:41.54,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider! Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.04,0:24:45.79,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Comment: 0,0:02:04.24,0:02:09.25,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs135\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\1c&HF3F4F4&\b1\pos(487.167,700.389)}Monstrous Merman Amazonia